    "There is a plethora of manual image analysis tools but in this review we will focus on automatic or semi-automatic quantification.",
    "Anatomically, the brain is compartmentalized into distinct regions, each with designated functions that collectively contribute to a range of high-order cognitive processes.",
    "Inter-regional brain connectomics consists of mapping and studying the complex networks between different regions (Behrens and Sporns, 2012).",
    "By analyzing these connections, using either macro, meso, or multiscale imaging strategies, it is possible to gain insights into how different regions cooperate or compete (Behrens and Sporns, 2012), and how disruptions in these networks may lead to neurological or psychiatric disorders.",
